# ─── "Rahasia Dapur" / Internal Notes ─────────────────────────────────
# All Markdown files are internal-only by default. Explicit anchors for
# the README exceptions so they re-include at root AND any subdirectory
# (the most-tested GitHub pattern).
*.md
!/README.md
!**/README.md

